Last Updated: November 2025
Application: HumAIr

This Privacy Policy explains how the HumAIr application (‚ÄúApp‚Äù) collects, uses, and protects your personal data.

By using the App, you agree to this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect

1.1 Account Information

When you create an account, the following information is collected:

- Email address  
- Password (hashed only; never stored as plain text)  
- Account creation date  
- Credit balance  
- Purchase history (via RevenueCat)

1.2 Uploaded Chat Files (Chat Export)

HumAIr allows you to upload exported .txt chat files from applications such as WhatsApp.

These files are:

- Temporarily transmitted to the server solely for analysis  
- Permanently deleted immediately after processing  
- Never stored long-term or retained by us  
- Never shared with other users, third parties, or the developer

Chat file content is used exclusively to generate AI analysis and is not processed for any other purpose.

2. On-Device Data Storage

- Uploaded chat files are stored locally on your device
- No copies of your chat data are kept on our servers
- We cannot access your chat data unless it remains on your device
- The App does not provide any remote access to your chat history

HumAIr is designed with a ‚Äúprivacy-first local processing‚Äù approach.

3. Server-Side Processing

On our servers, the following steps occur:

- The .txt file is received
- The file is forwarded to the AI service for analysis
- The AI result is generated and returned to the App
- The uploaded file is immediately deleted

No chat data is:

- Stored  
- Backed up  
- Archived  
- Transferred to third parties  
- Used for service improvement or training

4. AI Processing

AI analysis is generated using the Google Gemini API.

Only the necessary text segments are sent to Gemini.
No personally identifiable information (email, device data, etc.) is transmitted.

According to Google‚Äôs policies, submitted content is not used to train their models.

All analyses are for entertainment purposes only.

