These services do not store your chat files.

6. Data Retention

- Account data ‚Üí retained until account deletion
- Chat files ‚Üí deleted immediately after analysis
- Logs ‚Üí retained for a limited time (does not include chat data)
- Payment and credit records ‚Üí stored by Apple App Store / Google Play

7. Data Deletion Requests

You may request deletion of your data via:

- Using the ‚ÄúDelete Account‚Äù feature in the App
- Sending an email to: humairapp@gmail.com

Upon deletion request:

- Your account will be removed  
- No chat data remains on our servers  
- Personal information will be permanently erased within 30 days

